decl sym_t1(t1, gt1)
sym_t1.val = x * x
sym_t1.grad = gt1
decl sym_y(y, gy)
sym_y.val = t1 * x
sym_y.grad = 1
---backward--
dep link:
sym_y -> sym_t1 -> sym_x
sym_x -> (x, gx)
gx -> (x, sym_t1, sym_y)
